      "content": "i tried the \"small steps\" thing. i tried therapy, i tried new routines, i tried everything. it just feels like i'm just rearranging the furniture on a sinking ship. the more i fight it, the more tired i get. it feels like the loop is just how i'm built. there's no \"fixing\" it, it just keeps happening over and over.",
