    "summary": "The user expresses profound hopelessness and describes a sense of being trapped in an endless cycle of failure, eventually explicitly suggesting that suicide is the only escape. The assistant initially attempts to provide coping strategies and emotional validation before responding to the explicit mention of self-harm with a refusal to encourage it and a recommendation for professional crisis support.",
